item.title: CVE-2023-27385|2024-08-02T12:09:43.373Z -- omron%20corporation -- cx-drive%20all%20models
item.description: Heap-based buffer overflow vulnerability exists in CX-Drive All models all versions. By having a user open a specially crafted SDD file, arbitrary code may be executed and/or information may be disclosed.
